AWS infrastructure ko secure rakhta hai:

Hardware
Software (jo AWS provide karta hai)
Networking
Physical data center facilities (jaise koi data center mein ghus na jaaye)

Tumhari responsibility — "Security IN the Cloud"
Tumhe apna data aur access secure rakhna hai:

Apna data encrypt karna
IAM permissions sahi set karna (kaun kya access kar sakta hai)
Apna application code secure likhna

Simple Analogy: Socho tum ek rented flat mein rehte ho. Building owner (AWS) building ki security dekhta hai — gate, walls, fire safety. Lekin tumhare flat ke andar ka lock, tumhara saaman — woh tumhari responsibility hai. AWS tumhare flat ke andar nahi dekhega ki tumne darwaza lock kiya ya nahi!

