Amazon SNS- SImple Notification service
What is Amazon SNS?
Amazon simple Notification service(SNS) is a fully managed messaging service for sending messages to multiple recipients(subscribers). It decouples distributed systems and microservices, and can send notifications to users via SMS, mobile push, or email.

SNS Features
Message Endpoints
SNS can publish messages to:
HTTP/HTTPS
Emails
Amazon SQS
AWS Lambda
Mobile applications
SMS(region-dependent)
